# Billy - Full-Stack React + Cloudflare Workers Application

## Project Architecture

This is a full-stack application called "Billy" that combines:
- **Frontend**: React 19 + Vite + TanStack Router + Tailwind CSS
- **Backend**: Hono framework running on Cloudflare Workers
- **Database**: Cloudflare D1 (SQLite) with Drizzle ORM
- **Bot**: Telegram bot integration using Grammy
- **AI**: Google AI SDK integration
- **Deployment**: Cloudflare Workers platform

